race.comment: GOLDEN ENVY (2) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 2 lengths (24.19) behind COSMIC BEACH at this track. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and three minor placings from five starts. Deserves serious consideration. PLAY DIRTY (5) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (24.08) and beaten half a length over 407m at this track. Can measure up. RIDING SOLO (4) missed the frame latest (24.26) when fourth over 407m at this track in a Free For All. Looks one of the chances. VELOCITY COMMIT (3) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
